<cu-custom bgColor="bg-gradual-purple">
  <view slot="content">今日快讯</view>
</cu-custom>
<view>
  <swiper
    indicator-dots="true"
    autoplay="true"
    interval="2000"
  >
    <swiper-item><image src="/images/swiper/1.jpg"></image></swiper-item>
    <swiper-item><image src="/images/swiper/2.png"></image></swiper-item>
    <swiper-item><image src="/images/swiper/3.png"></image></swiper-item>
  </swiper>

  <view class="cu-card ">
    <view class="cu-item item_con">
      <view class="cu-list menu-avatar">
        <view class="cu-item">
          <view class="cu-avatar round lg" style="background-image:url(https://ossweb-img.qq.com/images/lol/web201310/skin/big10006.jpg);"></view>
          <view class="content flex-sub">
            <view class="text-gray text-sm flex justify-between">
              {{ date }}
            </view>
          </view>
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="grid flex-sub padding-lr" class="col-3">
      <view class="text-content item_title">
        冰山撞岛屿，并不是一场美丽邂逅。
      </view>
        <view class="bg-img" style="background-image:url(https://p4.img.cctvpic.com/photoworkspace/2020/11/26/2020112611331486119.jpg);height:200px;">
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="text-content item_text">
        巨型冰山A68于2017年从南极拉森-C冰架上脱离，现在由这座冰山分裂出的A68a冰山正朝着大西洋南部的野生动物天堂南乔治亚岛漂移，将于本月底或下月初漂移至位于大西洋的南乔治亚岛近海，并且有可能会与乔治亚岛发生碰撞。
      </view>
      <view class="text-gray text-sm text-right padding">
        <text class="cuIcon-attentionfill margin-lr-xs"></text> 10
        <text class="cuIcon-appreciatefill margin-lr-xs"></text> 20
        <text class="cuIcon-messagefill margin-lr-xs"></text> 30
      </view>

    </view>
  </view>

</view>